    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If we add to djConfig "parseOnLoad = true" and we use programmatic style, in the auto created addOnLoad method the parser is ran manually.</p>

<p>So the first time, when the dom is ready the dojo parser runs (due to parseOnLoad = true) and just after, the zend method run the parser again (auto generated method).</p>

